Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:09.75,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never tell what he was thinking, so I had to finish with him
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:13.01,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? So, after that, what happened with your dad?
