Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could have been fun, if you'd been a little smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show the world what happens when you cross me, L.
