Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five seconds... Four.. {\alpha&HFF&}Three.. Two.. One..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five seconds... Four.. Three.. {\alpha&HFF&}Two.. One..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five seconds... Four.. Three.. Two.. {\alpha&HFF&}One..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five seconds... Four.. Three.. Two.. One..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? {\alpha&HFF&}Now, what do you have to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Now, what do you have to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tested it just in case, {\alpha&HFF&}but I never thought it could actually be true..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tested it just in case, but I never thought it could actually be true..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}it seems you can kill people without having to be there in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, it seems you can kill people without having to be there in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have been able to believe this if I hadn't just witnessed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely, Kira; {\alpha&HFF&}if you did indeed kill the "Lind L. Tailor" on screen, I can tell you that he was in fact a criminal that was due to be put to death today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely, Kira; if you did indeed kill the "Lind L. Tailor" on screen, {\alpha&HFF&}I can tell you that he was in fact a criminal that was due to be put to death today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely, Kira; if you did indeed kill the "Lind L. Tailor" on screen, I can tell you that he was in fact a criminal that was due to be put to death today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have heard of him on the news or through the Internet. {\alpha&HFF&}He was a criminal that was captured by the police in absolute secrecy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have heard of him on the news or through the Internet. He was a criminal that was captured by the police in absolute secrecy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like not even you have information on these kinds of killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He definitely got ya this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as for L, {\alpha&HFF&}he certainly does exist, as my own persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as for L, he certainly does exist, as my own persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, {\alpha&HFF&}try and kill me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, try and kill me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-{\alpha&HFF&}You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill yourself, L?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taunting Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}don't read this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? {\alpha&HFF&}Can't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Can't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it seems you can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there are certain people you can't kill. {\alpha&HFF&}Thanks for the hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there are certain people you can't kill. Thanks for the hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a reward, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll tell you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a reward, I'll tell you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lied about this being a live worldwide broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This announcement is currently only being broadcast across the Kanto region of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were planning to broadcast it at different times, across different regions, {\alpha&HFF&}but it seems that there is no longer any need for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were planning to broadcast it at different times, across different regions, but it seems that there is no longer any need for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in Kanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this guy, L, is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first killing was overlooked by the police as it was such a small incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, your first victim was in fact the phantom killer in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While the other high profile criminals were dying of heart attacks, {\alpha&HFF&}this was the one incident that stuck out as being quite a heavy punishment for a relatively low profile crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While the other high profile criminals were dying of heart attacks, this was the one incident that stuck out as being quite a heavy punishment for a relatively low profile crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, {\alpha&HFF&}that incident was only reported within Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, that incident was only reported within Japan.
